West Reading Galaxy - Fantasy Football 2011

Installation Instructions...

1) Download Via Git
2) bundle install
3) edit conf/database.yml
4) rake db:migrate
5) run Player.full_update from the console

Adding teams to the database

1) Edit to lib/team_data.yml with the current team data, see file for file format
2) run Team.load_yaml_team_data from the console
3) Note this will destroy all existing member and players associations for any existing teams, but doesn't matter as long as you didn't delete any data from the YAML file
